toc":672},"root",[183,199,205,213,218,223,232,237,242,247,252,257,262,297,311,316,321,328,333,338,345,350,362,369,374,379,384,389,396,401,406,413,418,440,445,452,457,464,469,476,481,488,502,507,512,517,524,529,536,541,552,557,564,569,576,583,588,595,600,607,612,619,624,631,636,643,648,655,660,667],{"type":184,"tag":185,"props":186,"children":188},"element","h2",{"id":187},"twitter",[189],{"type":184,"tag":190,"props":191,"children":195},"a",{"href":192,"rel":193},"https://x.com/budibase?utm_campaign=Onboarding&utm_medium=email&_hsenc=p2ANqtz--6Ynd76E4FehE07-MjjIZWwvuH2B-KMkxdBPT1TJ5Eh4ci9Wy0q_RZYTIRBsGXz_09u4n_C8GiUe9f8mFjiC6Dj9B4sw&_hsmi=66516363&utm_content=66516363&utm_source=hs_automation",[194],"nofollow",[196],{"type":197,"value":198},"text","Twitter",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":201,"children":202},"p",{},[203],{"type":197,"value":204},"2020 年那会儿 Budibase 从 SlackHQ 迁移到 Discord，发布了他的第一条推文，尽管点赞数量只有寥寥三个。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":206,"children":207},{},[208],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":210,"children":212},"img",{"alt":178,"src":211},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031913704.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":214,"children":215},{},[216],{"type":197,"value":217},"推崇 Sarah Drasner 的空盒子概念，即“也许我们可以从一个空盒子开始，这个盒子只包含正在解决的问题的核心用例或问题”，而不是看到周围完整的网站或应用而感到自卑。Budibase 认为它是一个空盒子，为用户抽象了构建 Web 应用的复杂性。PRay 也是如此，并且应当在多用户交互上大有改进。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":219,"children":220},{},[221],{"type":197,"value":222},"Joe Johnston（应该是 budibase 成员）在 2020 年发表了 What is custom software development in 2025，讨论了“定制化软件开发”需求的广阔场景。",{"type":184,"tag":224,"props":225,"children":226},"blockquote",{},[227],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":228,"children":229},{},[230],{"type":197,"value":231},"定制软件开发是指为特定问题、用户或人群设计、开发、部署、维护和提供软件支持的过程。理解定制软件开发的关键在于认识到正在开发的解决方案是为单一、特定的目的/问题量身定制的——通常无法通过现有的解决方案来解决。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":233,"children":234},{},[235],{"type":197,"value":236},"SaaS 软件（COTS 商业现货软件）单价比定制低，但远没有定制乃至自建来得灵活。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":238,"children":239},{},[240],{"type":197,"value":241},"“when COTS software did not solve the problem for SMEs, tools like Excel and Access were drafted in and a solution glued together”，Excel 作为从业者的信息交换工具，类似 Python、Lua 在游戏引擎中的胶水作用。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":243,"children":244},{},[245],{"type":197,"value":246},"今天正好是 2025 年 1 月，我认为 budibase 对软件开发的认识很有前瞻性。其观点也符合我的两点认识：第一，软件开发应该面向更广阔的 C 端，在知识爆炸并有势形成超级个体的时代，代码技能（实际上是指通过人机界面制定规则并实现需求）是全民必备的技能；第二，新时代的消费包含了新时代的创造，消费时间不仅仅通过娱乐，也可以包含创造性的方式，如同我的世界、乐高等。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":248,"children":249},{},[250],{"type":197,"value":251},"文章引用了 Percolate、Oribi、Monese 三个工具来说明定制软件如何解决问题，但没用过评价不了。实际上这可能只是为了文章的 SEO。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":253,"children":254},{},[255],{"type":197,"value":256},"2020-10-02 发布了一个暗黑风格的界面，是制作内容的暗黑风格，而不是 budibase 的。其本地的暗黑模式是在 2020-11-06 号发布的（已经过了公测前两周），不过这速度也太快了。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":258,"children":259},{},[260],{"type":197,"value":261},"有人发推推荐了一些产品，包括 budibase，剩下一些可能值得观摩的：",{"type":184,"tag":263,"props":264,"children":265},"ul",{},[266,277,287],{"type":184,"tag":267,"props":268,"children":269},"li",{},[270],{"type":184,"tag":190,"props":271,"children":274},{"href":272,"rel":273},"https://x.com/PoryHQ",[194],[275],{"type":197,"value":276},"PoryHQ",{"type":184,"tag":267,"props":278,"children":279},{},[280],{"type":184,"tag":190,"props":281,"children":284},{"href":282,"rel":283},"https://x.com/bildrHQ",[194],[285],{"type":197,"value":286},"bildrHQ",{"type":184,"tag":267,"props":288,"children":289},{},[290],{"type":184,"tag":190,"props":291,"children":294},{"href":292,"rel":293},"https://x.com/draftbit",[194],[295],{"type":197,"value":296},"draftbit",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":298,"children":299},{},[300,302,309],{"type":197,"value":301},"有个 Tag 叫做 ",{"type":184,"tag":303,"props":304,"children":306},"code",{"className":305},[],[307],{"type":197,"value":308},"#100DaysOfNoCode",{"type":197,"value":310},"，看着不错。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":312,"children":313},{},[314],{"type":197,"value":315},"Bubibase 推荐了 Martin McKeveney 的 NoSQL 和 DynamoDB 的演讲。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":317,"children":318},{},[319],{"type":197,"value":320},"展示了一些预制的渐变色（UI 还可以优化）：",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":322,"children":323},{},[324],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":325,"children":327},{"alt":178,"src":326},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031950748.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":329,"children":330},{},[331],{"type":197,"value":332},"2020-10-22 发布了不推荐生产环境使用的公共测试版本。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":334,"children":335},{},[336],{"type":197,"value":337},"在什么是你建 Web App 时最喜欢的工作内容时，没有人投票给“测试”。不过，反向思考，能辅助用户做测试的工具可能也是很有市场的。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":339,"children":340},{},[341],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":342,"children":344},{"alt":178,"src":343},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501031954506.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":346,"children":347},{},[348],{"type":197,"value":349},"TechCrunch 的一篇 The No-Code Generation is arriving 文章中，根据“In the distant past, there was a proverbial “digital divide” that bifurcated workers into those who knew how to use computers and those who didn’t.”推演了今后数据分析工程在今后可能作为新的“数字鸿沟”出现以及带来的影响。而这正是过去几年（2017~2020）低代码发力的方向，AirTable 和 Retool 这种年轻的公司分别以 26 亿以及 10 亿美元的估值崛起。文章还提到了“而像 Bildr、Shogun、Bubble、Stacker”等公司，但是我没有用过。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":351,"children":352},{},[353,360],{"type":184,"tag":190,"props":354,"children":357},{"href":355,"rel":356},"https://nocodelist.co/",[194],[358],{"type":197,"value":359},"NocodeList",{"type":197,"value":361},"，收集了 300+ 无代码工具，而他本身就是一个很适合无代码建设的网站。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":363,"children":364},{},[365],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":366,"children":368},{"alt":178,"src":367},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032006061.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":370,"children":371},{},[372],{"type":197,"value":373},"数据看起来还不错，两周的公测信息。公测后两周的数据没有前两周好看。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":375,"children":376},{},[377],{"type":197,"value":378},"🔻 606 downloads\n🤖 619 apps created\n🚀 246 apps deployed",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":380,"children":381},{},[382],{"type":197,"value":383},"在公测第三个月时，bb 积累了 3200+ 用户、2400+ 应用，以及 554 个部署的应用。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":385,"children":386},{},[387],{"type":197,"value":388},"2020-11-09 发布的图表功能，第一版的功能比较简单，但是很有视觉风格：",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":390,"children":391},{},[392],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":393,"children":395},{"alt":178,"src":394},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032011651.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":397,"children":398},{},[399],{"type":197,"value":400},"2020-12-20 称自己是“open organization”，可以在 Github 上看到他们的项目路线图，甚至是参与讨论。这种事情（类似完成度的产品）在国内就算放到 2025 年也很难想象。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":402,"children":403},{},[404],{"type":197,"value":405},"2020-12-09 在 budibase，15 分钟就能创造一个 Winamp 风格的界面。也许包括功能？链接打不开了，无法验证。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":407,"children":408},{},[409],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":410,"children":412},{"alt":178,"src":411},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032144479.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":414,"children":415},{},[416],{"type":197,"value":417},"“将 Star 数量视为开源社区的货币”这一信念让 Joe Johnston 开始 budibase 的 Github 星星之旅。在 11~12 月间，其数量从 83 个增长到了接近 500，在图上来看这就是指数级别的增长！在博客中分享了其做法。时间来到次年 2 月，Star 数量超过 2000，两倍超越了他们的去年的既定目标。",{"type":184,"tag":263,"props":419,"children":420},{},[421,425,430,435],{"type":184,"tag":267,"props":422,"children":423},{},[424],{"type":197,"value":198},{"type":184,"tag":267,"props":426,"children":427},{},[428],{"type":197,"value":429},"邮件引导指向 Github 并告知路线图、代码都在 Github",{"type":184,"tag":267,"props":431,"children":432},{},[433],{"type":197,"value":434},"budibase 制作的项目支持 Github 调用",{"type":184,"tag":267,"props":436,"children":437},{},[438],{"type":197,"value":439},"更新 Readme",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":441,"children":442},{},[443],{"type":197,"value":444},"而他们新的 Readme 也确实很有吸引力（“Build business apps 50x faster”）：",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":446,"children":447},{},[448],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":449,"children":451},{"alt":178,"src":450},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032149799.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":453,"children":454},{},[455],{"type":197,"value":456},"“As companies, we often look outwards for growth, but looking inwards can provide opportunities. Optimizing processes, analyzing data, & equipping staff with the right tools is often an easier win for many companies; this is where low-code platforms will continue to succeed.”，最有意思的配图。包括上文提到的 2025 软件定制需求前瞻一文中的配图，都是相同类型的矢量图，很有意思。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":458,"children":459},{},[460],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":461,"children":463},{"alt":178,"src":462},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032152157.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":465,"children":466},{},[467],{"type":197,"value":468},"2021 年初，关于希望使用哪个平台托管 bb，居然没有 AWS。前两名 Heroku 和 DigitalOcean 几乎占据了 100% 的投票。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":470,"children":471},{},[472],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":473,"children":475},{"alt":178,"src":474},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032154794.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":477,"children":478},{},[479],{"type":197,"value":480},"还有另一个投票也显示了 Twitter 上用户的数据库偏好，第一名居然是 Google Sheets。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":482,"children":483},{},[484],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":485,"children":487},{"alt":178,"src":486},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032156394.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":489,"children":490},{},[491,493,500],{"type":197,"value":492},"推荐了一个如何启动开源项目并扩大其影响力的网站，里面有一系列文章：",{"type":184,"tag":190,"props":494,"children":497},{"href":495,"rel":496},"https://opensource.guide/",[194],[498],{"type":197,"value":499},"Open Source Guides",{"type":197,"value":501},"。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":503,"children":504},{},[505],{"type":197,"value":506},"Tech Nation 的 Rising Stars 3 奖项包含了 bb。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":508,"children":509},{},[510],{"type":197,"value":511},"2021-04-13 招聘 3 名 JavaScript 工程师。基于之前他发过关于 Svelte 的迷因，我猜创始人对 Svelte 依旧比较感兴趣。同月 25 号，bb 赞助了 Svelte Summit。直到次年 1 月，他们才开始招聘产品负责人、JS 工程师、产品教育经历、产品设计和客户成功经理，可见扩张得比较节制。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":513,"children":514},{},[515],{"type":197,"value":516},"那么，下一步是什么？我也想问。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":518,"children":519},{},[520],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":521,"children":523},{"alt":178,"src":522},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032244873.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":525,"children":526},{},[527],{"type":197,"value":528},"百姓网的知识库里面也有很多内部应用，但是年久失修。我管他们叫幽灵应用。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":530,"children":531},{},[532],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":533,"children":535},{"alt":178,"src":534},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032251644.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":537,"children":538},{},[539],{"type":197,"value":540},"2021-10-22 发布了新的响应式拖拽，看起来用户体验很好。PRay 马上跟进。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":542,"children":543},{},[544],{"type":184,"tag":545,"props":546,"children":549},"video",{"src":547,"controls":177,"width":548},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032256999.mp4","100%",[550],{"type":197,"value":551},"Your browser does not support the video tag.",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":553,"children":554},{},[555],{"type":197,"value":556},"不过 bb 的界面很总是看起来很“Notion”。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":558,"children":559},{},[560],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":561,"children":563},{"alt":178,"src":562},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032308303.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":565,"children":566},{},[567],{"type":197,"value":568},"2021-11-16 日，“经过两年的开发，我们激动的宣布正式在 product hunt 上进行官方宣传”。而他们的商业化也确实非常成功。2022-10-03 甚至创办了 5000 刀的低代码马拉松。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":570,"children":571},{},[572],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":573,"children":575},{"alt":178,"src":574},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032310378.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":577,"children":578},{},[579],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":580,"children":582},{"alt":178,"src":581},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032318431.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":584,"children":585},{},[586],{"type":197,"value":587},"这一切可能都归功于低代码的魔法。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":589,"children":590},{},[591],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":592,"children":594},{"alt":178,"src":593},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032320756.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":596,"children":597},{},[598],{"type":197,"value":599},"其中有非常长的一段时间，他们的 Twitter 都是围绕推广和新闻展开，没有其他内容的讨论。直到 2022-11 左右。此时，他们拿到了 @SignalFire 领投的 700 万美元融资。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":601,"children":602},{},[603],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":604,"children":606},{"alt":178,"src":605},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032316070.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":608,"children":609},{},[610],{"type":197,"value":611},"拿到融资后，Belfast 决定扩大团队规模。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":613,"children":614},{},[615],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":616,"children":618},{"alt":178,"src":617},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032326207.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":620,"children":621},{},[622],{"type":197,"value":623},"Joe Johnston 解释了为何要从 nocode 转型 lowcode。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":625,"children":626},{},[627],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":628,"children":630},{"alt":178,"src":629},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032329318.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":632,"children":633},{},[634],{"type":197,"value":635},"2023 年有许多更新，比如键盘操作，ISO 27001 认证等。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":637,"children":638},{},[639],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":640,"children":642},{"alt":178,"src":641},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032336236.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":644,"children":645},{},[646],{"type":197,"value":647},"最近一年更新了许多教程，这段时间他们对外宣称自己是“表单创建工具”，并且在博客上也两次拿其他表单创建工具做对比。期间放出不少有意思的应用展示，比如 GPT 克隆（2024-03-11）：",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":649,"children":650},{},[651],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":652,"children":654},{"alt":178,"src":653},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032340672.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":656,"children":657},{},[658],{"type":197,"value":659},"在商业化上变得更加大胆，比如推出 Paid Only 功能。",{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":661,"children":662},{},[663],{"type":184,"tag":209,"props":664,"children":666},{"alt":178,"src":665},"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202501032343927.png",[],{"type":184,"tag":200,"props":668,"children":669},{},[670],{"type":197,"value":671},"在最近（2024-11）的 3.0 更新中，他们解释了之后的路线，主要会包含 AI 相关功能的改进。",{"title":178,"searchDepth":673,"depth":673,"links":674},2,[675],{"id":187,"depth":673,"text":198},"markdown","content:6.maps:_products:budibase.md","content","6.maps/_products/budibase.md","6.maps/_products/budibase","md",[683,687],{"_path":684,"title":685,"description":686},"/maps/_products/bit","Bit","Bit 是一个组件驱动的开发工具，它可以帮助我们更好地管理组件。",{"_path":688,"title":689,"description":690},"/maps/_products/dynamo","Dynamo","Dynamo 原本是 Revit 中建筑信息模型 (BIM) 的附加模块，后来发展成熟，成为一个给设计师探索可视化编程、解决问题并自行制作工具的平台。",1771696727385]